Create symbolic links to the appropriate folders and dot files:
Make sure you have a .bash_aliases and .vimviews

/vim                --> ~/.vim
/bash/bashrc        --> ~/.bashrc
/bash/bash_aliases  --> ~/.bash_aliases
/vim/vimrc          --> ~/.vimrc
/git/git.config     --> ~/.git.config
/tmux.conf          --> ~/.tmux.conf

zsh
/zsh/custom         --> ~/.oh-my-zsh/custom
/zsh/zshrc          --> ~/.zshrc


